Vehicles, including cars and buses, traverse the road, adding a dynamic element to the otherwise static cityscape. The street itself is lined with trees, their green foliage providing a touch of nature amidst the concrete jungle. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a testament to the city's infrastructure.
